Title: CS-550: Advanced Computer Architecture
Body: Date: Wed, 20 Nov 1996 21:42:06 GMT Server: NCSA/1.5 Content-type: text/html CS-550: Advanced Computer Architecture Boston University / CAS Computer Science Dept CLA CS-550: Advanced Computer Architecture CS-550 overviews the concepts underlying the design of high-performance computer architectures, with an emphasis on quantitative evaluation and the interplay between computer architecture and the design of compilers and operating systems.
